Your sole priority is protecting the station, the Ifrit, and the transports until everyone's safely away. ADEIS seems focused on the station, but the LNA pilots have reported some drones breaking off to harass the evac ships. Per Captain Jers, no GTA ship is to engage IN.E.D.A.M.01 directly. We can't risk it deciding to accelerate its timetable while Amanu Station is still vulnerable."
