8975, "(fr)The faster we clear the jamming, the sooner we get reinforcements. I'm going banzai!"
8976, "(fr)Best plan so far. Geometry hot!"
8977, "(fr)Mayday, mayday, mayday! Anyone receiving this, come in! We're under attack!"
