11231, "(fr)Welcome to SCS-2-Alpha, Command Training. In this simulation, you will learn to coordinate with allied assets in battle."
11232, "(fr)The first order you'll learn is requesting cover. Open your comms board, select Ships, and then Alpha 2. Finally, select Cover Me. Check your directive list for the details. If you make a mistake, press Escape to close it."
11233, "(fr)Good. A drone is arriving. Order me to attack it."
11234, "(fr)Well done. How did it feel to order your first kill?"
11235, "(fr)Usually, you'll give orders to ships already in the mission, but sometimes you can call in others. You've already seen how to call in support ships$semicolon this time, you'll call in reinforcements. Open your comms board, select Reinforcements, and call in Bêta wing."
11236, "(fr)We're going to run a simulated convoy escort. Three cargo ships have been added to the simulation. Add each of them to your escort list. [Target and press $Alt-E$]"
11237, "(fr)Usually, your flight computer will detect and register important ships, but adding and removing them from the list is sometimes useful. You can also track all ships in the battlespace and assign custom hotkeys to them. [Press F3]"
11238, "(fr)Order me to protect either of the Poseidon-class freighters. Then, use the Wings option to tell Bêta wing to protect the Elysium-class transport. Poseidons have much tougher defenses, so the Elysium can use the help."
11239, "(fr)Use the Wings section of your comms board for this exercise."
11240, "(fr)The convoy is starting to move. Form up and join the escort. You may want to use your afterburner to close the distance."
11241, "(fr)A pirate scout has arrived to spy on the convoy. Open your comms board and order All Fighters to attack it."
11242, "(fr)Your wingmates are returning to their previously assigned orders. Once they're in position, we'll start the next phase of this simulation."
11243, "(fr)I've unlocked your weapons. Work with your wingmates to keep pirates away from the convoy. Our fighters cannot be destroyed, but will be temporarily knocked out upon taking critical damage."
11244, "(fr)Pirate fighters have arrived."
11245, "(fr)Pirate bombers are targeting Lambda 2. Use your bomb targeting control [$B$] to find them, and reassign guard orders as needed."
11246, "(fr)The pirate command ship has jumped in to attack the convoy. Your wingmates have been restored to full hull integrity and ammunition. Order them to disarm the Kingpin. You can also use a Destroy Subsystem order to call attacks on individual subsystems."
11247, "(fr)The Kingpin has been disarmed. Normally, we'd deploy a capture transport, but since this is a simulation, let's have some fun. Order all fighters to destroy the Kingpin!"
11248, "(fr)Well done. Enter subspace to end this simulator session when ready."
11249, "(fr)A convoy ship has fallen below 50% hull integrity. Check your escort list and reassign guard orders as needed."
11283, "(fr)The GTD Triumphant has arrived to celebrate your victory. Land in the Triumphant's fighterbay when you're ready [press $S$]."
